import React, { useEffect } from "react"
import axios from "axios"




function Form() {

    function submitNewUglyThing() {

        useEffect(() => {
            axios.post("https://api.vschool.io/chrismiller/thing")

        })
    }

    function onChange() { }

    return (
        <main>
            <form onSubmit={submitNewUglyThing}>
                <input
                    type="text"
                    placeholder="Title"
                >

                </input>

                <input
                    type="text"
                    placeholder="Img Url"
                >

                </input>

                <input
                    type="text"
                    placeholder="Description">
                </input>

                <button type="submit">Submit</button>
            </form>
        </main >
    )
}

export default Form
